      <title>寒冷天气预期导致德国电力跃升至一年来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/german-power-jumps-to-highest-in-a-year-on-cold-weather-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于预测气温下降和可再生能源产量下降，德国电价升至一年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
